{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c30ee90e35","title":"关于“我的忧虑和呼吁”的说明","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9cfdf67808","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":2,"articleId":"c30ee90e35"}],"tags":[{"id":"8ea55d34c1","name":"胡耀邦","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"1b6d6991fb","name":"叶于泩"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"49101c4328","type":"title","text":"关于“我的忧虑和呼吁”的说明","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"b00cba9312","type":"authors","text":"北京大学叶于泩","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"532857d978","type":"subtitle","text":"（叶于泩：北京大学哲学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"5912f3f591","type":"paragraph","text":"一、本文不企图证明什么，只是写出作者个人的忧虑！以及基于忧虑的呼吁、列举诸“迹象”是为了说明忧虑的原因。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"4b529fdc5e","type":"paragraph","text":"二、迹象的说明：（逐条解释）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"405303ad71","type":"paragraph","text":"①鸣放方针提出之初，有百分之九十高干不同意。见林希翎致马老公开倌。和潘家威“论目前民主运动及其领导”，既然无人反驳，当属事实。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"2492f9f7d3","type":"paragraph","text":"②北大处于无政府状态等，见民主墙南开同学来信。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"942d1d75d4","type":"paragraph","text":"③北大闹的比波匈事件还凶……是林希翎说的我有几分相信，故列为“迹象”，冠以据说。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"6591a4d978","type":"paragraph","text":"④有人要毛主席下台……潘家威同学谈，这话是胡耀邦说的，有人写信给毛主席，要他下台等。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"ee38719bc4","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤贯彻鸣放障碍重重，至今……，个人读报，观察结果。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"5a0695ef53","type":"paragraph","text":"⑥胡耀邦谈当家难等是潘家威等六人，访问胡时，胡谈，并见潘文“论当前民主运动及其领导”。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"2625ce4823","type":"paragraph","text":"⑦反对鸣放有我们熟悉的领导者在内，出处同上条。据潘此系友人告知，已答应保密，不便道出姓名。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"492b5bd315","type":"paragraph","text":"⑧陆定一、彭德怀谈话，见中国青年报，人民日报。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"ceead69fa6","type":"paragraph","text":"⑨苏联转戴陈其通文，“教条主义”是我校传达毛主席报告时说的。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"7a09f405bc","type":"paragraph","text":"⑩苏联对鸣放冷淡是我读报观察所得。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"61e165811c","type":"paragraph","text":"⑾我校领导落后于群众，是个人观察结果。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"},{"id":"083f187ff6","type":"paragraph","text":" 叶于泩57年6月2日","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35"}],"page":{"id":"cfb30a3035","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c30ee90e35","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}